OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1779563472
OL,3,CConfusion over whether Guernsey really
OL,4,Cis in a financial crisis
OL,6,FSome politicians and tax experts in
OL,7,FGuernsey say the recent revelation
OL,8,Fthat the island was in surplus by more
OL,9,Fthan #100 million throws plans for a
OL,10,F5% goods and services tax (GST) into
OL,11,Fdoubt.
OL,13,FFor years people in Guernsey have been
OL,14,Ftold that the island has a structural
OL,15,Fdeficit with most recent figures
OL,16,Fputting that at #78 million.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
