CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1779563472
OL,3,CConfusion over whether Guernsey really
OL,4,Cis in a financial crisis
OL,6,FThe island's top committee Policy and
OL,7,FResources (P&R) have now committed to
OL,8,Fbringing in tax reforms, this could
OL,9,Finclude a GST, but is also likely to
OL,10,Finclude other tax reforms.
OL,12,FBut Charles Parkinson who sits on P&R
OL,13,Fsays that the public finances are
OL,14,Factually 'robust'.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1779563472
OL,3,CConfusion over whether Guernsey really
OL,4,Cis in a financial crisis
OL,6,FHe said: "I think it is an open
OL,7,Fquestion about how much tax we need
OL,8,Fand I tend to push back when people
OL,9,Ftalk about a structural deficit. I
OL,10,Fdon't think you can talk about the
OL,11,Fstructural deficit when we're in
OL,12,Fhealth surplus."
OL,14,F"My take on this is yes there are
OL,15,Fserious issues that do need to be
OL,16,Fconsidered, yes we probably do need
OL,17,Fmore resources going forward. But
OL,18,Fwe're not in crisis."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1779563472
OL,3,CConfusion over whether Guernsey really
OL,4,Cis in a financial crisis
OL,6,FGraham Parrott, tax advisor, says
OL,7,Fthere is a lot of confusion over the
OL,8,Ffigures.
OL,10,FHe said: "My concern is that I'm not
OL,11,Fsure how many of our politicians
OL,12,Freally understand the numbers, and
OL,13,FI've got some sympathy with all of
OL,14,Fthis, because of the difficulty in
OL,15,Funderstanding the information and how
OL,16,Fvaried it is."
OL,18,F"We saw a headline just yesterday,
OL,19,Fsaying we have a #100 million surplus,
OL,20,Fso the response to that is going to be
OL,21,Fwhy do we need GST?"
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1779563472
OL,3,CConfusion over whether Guernsey really
OL,4,Cis in a financial crisis
OL,6,FP&R have said they are developing a
OL,7,Fblended package of tax reforms. They
OL,8,Fare looking at six areas of
OL,9,Fconsideration.
OL,11,FDeputy Lindsay de Sausmarez, President
OL,12,Fof P&R, said: "We are responding to
OL,13,Fthe legitimate concerns raised with a
OL,14,Fpackage that we believe finds the
OL,15,Fright blend of measures for this
OL,16,Fmoment in time."
OL,18,FShe added: "There is currently an
OL,19,Funderstandable assumption that we will
OL,20,Fsimply recommend the implementation of
OL,21,Fthe original GST-plus package.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1779563472
OL,3,CConfusion over whether Guernsey really
OL,4,Cis in a financial crisis
OL,6,F"Having looked at a range of different
OL,7,Fvariations and approaches, though, we
OL,8,Fare developing what we believe is a
OL,9,Fmore balanced blend of measures that
OL,10,Fdraws from each of the different
OL,11,Fworkstreams and responds
OL,12,Fproportionately and pragmatically to
OL,13,Fthe issues helpfully raised by the
OL,14,Fcommunity."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/7
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
